What is Sublime Text?

- A text editor to write code

Some Benefits:

-Multiple cursors
	- Vertical selector for Mac
		- option + up or down arrow
	- Selecting multiple instances of the same text
		- Select one at a time
			"command + d" on Mac - "ctrl + d" on Windows
		- Select all
			"control + command + g" on Mac - "Alt + F3" on Windows

-Sidebar to scroll
